data.description: Gorgeous newly built (2020) custom residence with rear garage and no HOA is available from the original owners! Exceptional care for this 3 bedroom 2 bath home is evident throughout!  Mid-century modern style with gorgeous polished concrete flooring, vaulted ceilings, and tons of windows, this will entertain even the pickiest of buyers! Open floorplan with a chef's kitchen complete with gorgeous two-toned cabinetry, and solid surface countertops, compliments the large living/dining room.  Natural light is abundant and welcoming! Master bedroom is split from the secondary bedrooms, offering peace and tranquility.  The garage is at the rear of the house with alley access, allowing the front to stand out with curb-appeal! Large, fenced in yard and above ground pool can entertain family and friends throughout the year!  Close to shopping, restaurants and the highway, this home stands out above the rest!  Schedule your private showing today!
